19
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:34,700
[Directed by Chen Zhoufei]

20
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:42,320
[Dashing Youth]

21
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:45,650
[Based on "Zhou Munan's
