22
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:49,020
[from fanqienovel.com and bkneng.com]

23
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:52,020
[Episode 20]

24
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:08,220
Ye,

25
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:11,020
do you still remember what I said

26
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:12,540
before we embarked on this journey?

27
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:14,260
Which sentence exactly?

28
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:18,060
Observe every strike I make carefully,

29
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,460
except for the last strike.

30
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:20,460
Otherwise,

31
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:21,980
it'd all go to waste.

32
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,340
I don't want to miss that strike.

33
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:38,140
My silly disciple.

34
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:41,700
Amid the trickling rain
and ethereal fog,

35
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:46,580
here I come treading on water.

36
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:11,620
[Yan Lingxia,
The Blade Deity of Nanjue]

37
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:33,500
Rain Demon.

38
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:35,740
You're here after all.

39
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,260
Chunshui,

40
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,060
what kind of person

41
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:43,380
is the Rain Demon like?

42
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:44,660
Is he going

43
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:45,940
to lead Yun astray?

44
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:47,900
During our journey,

45
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:49,380
I've heard a bunch
of martial artists talking about

46
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:51,140
how he's traveling to Nanjue with Yun.

47
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:53,660
The Rain Demon

48
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:55,300
had a nickname when he was young,

49
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,420
the Rain Maniac,

50
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:59,460
because he was maniacal and arrogant.

51
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:02,340
During his younger days
roaming the martial arts world,

52
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:03,260
he had defeated many people

53
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:05,100
who were actually stronger than him,

54
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:07,420
simply because he was a maniac.

55
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:09,140
Unfortunately,

56
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:12,060
he would eventually
encounter Li Changsheng.

57
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:15,020
And what kind of person
was Li Changsheng like?

58
00:04:15,780 --> 00:04:17,260
He's far more maniacal and arrogant
than the Rain Demon was.

59
00:04:17,340 --> 00:04:18,740
Can you stop flattering yourself

60
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:20,180
in such an obnoxiously indirect way?

61
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,380
You rascal.

62
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:23,340
Am I flattering myself?

63
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:25,380
I'm flattering Li Changsheng.

64
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:27,700
As I said,

65
00:04:28,220 --> 00:04:30,620
in this life, I want to be

66
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:32,300
a genteel scholar,

67
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,500
an elegant young man.

68
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:36,460
I shall steer clear of worldly affairs

69
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:40,420
and I shall only
appreciate beautiful ladies.

70
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:44,660
You're over 180 years old,

71
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:46,020
and you're thinking
of appreciating beautiful ladies?

72
00:04:46,580 --> 00:04:47,860
You're too old to do that.

73
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:07,780
Chunshui.

74
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,260
The Rain Demon

75
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:12,100
used to be a handsome man.

76
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:13,900
But when he was mastering
the Demon Deity Sword Techniques,

77
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:14,700
something happened,

78
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:16,500
and he turned into a beautiful woman.

79
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:22,180
See?

80
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:23,660
Unlike you,

81
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:25,660
he doesn't care much
about romantic affairs.

82
00:05:26,170 --> 00:05:27,690
Otherwise, he wouldn't have
traveled all the way

83
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:29,500
to kill Yan Lingxia.

84
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:31,660
Chunshui.

85
00:05:32,740 --> 00:05:33,780
What's the deal about Yan Lingxia?

86
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:43,380
Beautiful.

87
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:46,420
She's beautiful.

88
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:48,300
You really don't care if it's too old
to appreciate beautiful ladies.

89
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:53,700
Five li from here

90
00:05:54,380 --> 00:05:55,380
is a town

91
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:56,420
called Qianyue Town.

92
00:05:56,820 --> 00:05:58,740
We'll spend the night there.

93
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:40,180
Rain Demon,

94
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:42,260
we shouldn't have met today.

95
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:43,980
What a nag.

96
00:06:58,780 --> 00:06:59,700
Master, do you think

97
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:00,540
the Rain Demon

98
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:01,780
is any match for Yan Lingxia?

99
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:03,580
I can't say for certain.

100
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:05,660
I thought you knew everything.

101
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:07,140
What are you uncertain about?

102
00:07:07,980 --> 00:07:10,300
If he's doing this for himself,

103
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:12,780
I guess they'd probably

104
00:07:12,980 --> 00:07:14,260
end the fight in a draw.

105
00:07:15,020 --> 00:07:16,260
But, if he's doing this
for someone else...

106
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:19,100
You mean for Yun?

107
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:21,660
The Rain Demon

108
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:24,420
may be called a demon,

109
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:27,020
but to me,

110
00:07:28,180 --> 00:07:29,620
compared to most people, he's...

111
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:30,460
He's what?

112
00:07:36,140 --> 00:07:37,180
Kinder than anyone else.

113
00:07:54,020 --> 00:07:54,900
I have lost,

114
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:57,820
but you're about to die.

115
00:07:58,820 --> 00:07:59,820
You shouldn't have gone all out

116
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:01,300
just to pursue a title

117
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:03,020
as useless
as the top martial artist of Nanjue.

118
00:08:04,900 --> 00:08:07,060
I have never sought for such a title,

119
00:08:08,260 --> 00:08:10,260
even if the whole world
believes otherwise.

120
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,540
Let them believe what they want, then.

121
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:34,340
Ye.

122
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,620
I told you not to watch my last strike,

123
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,380
but...

124
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:45,740
You saw it, didn't you?

125
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:50,940
Master.

126
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:04,780
Ye,

127
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:07,460
don't be sad.

128
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:11,500
Don't avenge me either.

129
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:18,420
I have been practicing
the demonic art for so many years,

130
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:20,180
and my health

131
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:23,220
has already almost depleted.

132
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:27,260
Even if I don't die today,

133
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:30,620
I'd have less than six months to live.

134
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:35,500
Throughout this journey,

135
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:37,980
I have launched 13 strikes.

136
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,420
Every strike

137
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:45,180
has been a lesson for you.

138
00:09:51,060 --> 00:09:52,980
As your master...

139
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:55,860
this is

140
00:09:57,980 --> 00:09:59,580
all I can do for you.

141
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:03,740
Ye.

142
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:08,540
I didn't want you
to see the final strike

143
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:10,700
because I hoped you wouldn't

144
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,380
follow in my footsteps.

145
00:10:15,140 --> 00:10:15,820
But...

146
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:21,860
Since you saw it,

147
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:24,860
you will have to bear

148
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:26,540
the legacy of my sword fighting.

149
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:35,660
I have left you a letter.

150
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:38,820
There's an address on it.

151
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,700
Head to the address.

152
00:10:42,780 --> 00:10:43,460
Master.

153
00:10:45,420 --> 00:10:46,900
I have left a present for you.

154
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,460
Thank you, Master.

155
00:10:58,540 --> 00:11:01,060
There's an old geezer in the north

156
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:05,140
that I have never been able to defeat.

157
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:08,940
Make sure you train hard

158
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:11,460
and defeat his disciple.

159
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,060
I will remember that.

160
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:21,020
I shall not

161
00:11:23,020 --> 00:11:24,460
disappoint you.

162
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:28,460
Farewell,

163
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:30,780
Ye.

164
00:11:42,580 --> 00:11:44,260
No one knows where I, the Rain Demon,

165
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:45,420
comes from.

166
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:48,460
I also do not wish for anyone to know

167
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:51,380
where my final resting spot is.

168
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:09,100
Master!

169
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:30,340
Chunshui,

170
00:12:31,820 --> 00:12:32,540
what are you looking?

171
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:38,620
I can sense

172
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:42,300
an old friend departing somewhere.

173
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:07,820
Not bad.

174
00:13:08,540 --> 00:13:10,340
You can already take three hits from me.

175
00:13:11,340 --> 00:13:13,060
Sikong Changfeng, let's talk.

176
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:14,220
Sure.

177
00:13:16,460 --> 00:13:17,260
All this time,

178
00:13:17,420 --> 00:13:18,500
I've been meaning to ask you this.

179
00:13:19,180 --> 00:13:20,740
Baili Dongjun
is from the Marquis's Mansion

180
00:13:20,820 --> 00:13:21,700
and he has a noble status.

181
00:13:22,060 --> 00:13:23,300
His father is the Marquis's son

182
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:25,060
and his mother is
the young lady of the Wen Family.

183
00:13:25,660 --> 00:13:26,260
Right now, he's also

184
00:13:26,260 --> 00:13:27,860
a disciple of Li Changsheng,
the top martial artist.

185
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:30,140
He's lucky to have a good life,

186
00:13:31,220 --> 00:13:31,900
but you

187
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:33,100
have been wandering since young,

188
00:13:33,300 --> 00:13:35,020
without a place to call home.

189
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:36,380
Usually,

190
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:37,300
a rich kid like him

191
00:13:37,340 --> 00:13:38,620
would be someone that you'd detest,

192
00:13:38,940 --> 00:13:40,900
but why are you friends with him?

193
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:46,420
When I met him,

194
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:47,500
I didn't even know

195
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,500
he was from the Marquis's Mansion.

196
00:13:48,820 --> 00:13:49,900
Back then, all I thought was

197
00:13:50,420 --> 00:13:51,660
that we happened to meet by chance,

198
00:13:51,860 --> 00:13:52,820
and it's good to travel
around the martial arts world

199
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:53,500
together.

200
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:54,740
Even after

201
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,500
I knew that he's from
the Marquis's Mansion,

202
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:57,620
I realized

203
00:13:58,020 --> 00:13:59,660
that even someone
from the Marquis's Mansion

204
00:13:59,860 --> 00:14:00,820
could be like him.

205
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:03,140
Like how?

206
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:03,900
I have seen

207
00:14:03,900 --> 00:14:05,220
many people from noble families.

208
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:06,300
Most of them

209
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:07,620
may look decent outside,

210
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:09,740
but they have a dirty heart.

211
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:11,260
But Baili Dongjun is different.

212
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:13,180
His heart is as pure

213
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:14,180
as a youth's.

214
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:16,300
Nice answer.

215
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:18,180
Moreover,

216
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:19,500
I think that both of us

217
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:20,300
are of the same kind.

218
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:22,740
He's lucky to have a good life while I'm
lucky to not get killed easily.

219
00:14:23,180 --> 00:14:23,780
He and I

220
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:25,580
will reach our end goals eventually.

221
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:28,820
That's a marvelous answer.

222
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:31,700
We've been training for several days

223
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:33,140
and you've probably heard some rumors

224
00:14:33,220 --> 00:14:34,420
that I might take you in as my disciple.

225
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:36,180
Wait, sir.

226
00:14:36,700 --> 00:14:37,900
Those are just rumors.

227
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:39,860
I'm already glad that you're willing

228
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:41,340
to give me a few pointers.

229
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:42,580
I wouldn't dare to dream

230
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:44,100
of becoming your disciple.

231
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:45,660
I will not take you in as my disciple.

232
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:51,420
Because I'm not qualified.

233
00:14:51,980 --> 00:14:52,380
There's someone

234
00:14:52,380 --> 00:14:53,940
far more formidable than me

235
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:54,900
who wants to take you in
as his disciple,

236
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:57,020
but it's not the right time yet.

237
00:14:57,300 --> 00:14:59,180
That day will come soon, though.

238
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:01,220
He's also waiting

239
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:04,380
to meet you again
somewhere in this martial arts world.

240
00:15:05,100 --> 00:15:05,780
Meet me again?

241
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:07,420
Life is like a dream.

242
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:10,700
Meetings and partings come and go.

243
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:12,940
Are you leaving already, Mr. Xie?

244
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:15,100
As we have met, so must we part.

245
00:15:15,660 --> 00:15:16,700
I have finished reading,

246
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:18,260
so I have to go.

247
00:15:19,260 --> 00:15:19,980
Sikong,

248
00:15:20,540 --> 00:15:21,580
I hope we can also

249
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:23,500
meet again somewhere.

250
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:31,220
Martial Uncle.

251
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:41,700
Sir,

252
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:44,580
I think it's also time for me to go.

253
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:47,060
When are you leaving?

254
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:51,860
Right now, then.

255
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,180
You're so eager to leave, too?

256
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:56,180
Since I feel like venturing now,
why not?

257
00:15:56,860 --> 00:15:57,780
It's a big world outside.

258
00:15:58,100 --> 00:15:59,700
May we meet again, sir.

259
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,580
I'm off!

260
00:16:06,420 --> 00:16:07,740
This martial arts world remains the same

261
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:09,900
because of these youths

262
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:12,060
that continue to come
generation after generation.

263
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:23,460
We're here.

264
00:16:24,180 --> 00:16:24,740
This is it.

265
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:29,570
[Qianyue Smithy]

266
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:32,940
Chunshui.

267
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:34,580
Have you been here before?

268
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:36,540
What do you need? A hoe, a spade

269
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:37,060
or a plough?

270
00:16:37,420 --> 00:16:38,020
A blade.

271
00:16:39,020 --> 00:16:39,900
A good one.

272
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:46,020
Who are you?

273
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:47,500
An old friend.

274
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:48,780
What's your name?

275
00:16:48,900 --> 00:16:49,820
Nangong Chunshui.

276
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,620
Your surname isn't Li?

277
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:53,940
You look exactly the same

278
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:54,900
as that man when he was young.

279
00:16:55,340 --> 00:16:56,660
You're not his son?

280
00:17:00,340 --> 00:17:00,780
Why?

281
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:02,460
Does he look like

282
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:04,260
